{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.1","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:1","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les pa\u00efens<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-16: cf. (Mt 7:1-5. Ro 14:10-12.) Ga 6:7, 8. (Ja 1:22-25. Lu 12:47, 48. Ac 10:34, 35.) Ec 12:15, 16.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>O homme, qui que tu sois, toi qui juges, tu es donc inexcusable; car, en jugeant les autres, tu te condamnes toi-m\u00eame, puisque toi qui juges, tu fais les m\u00eames choses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.2","name":"Romains 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.32","name":"Romains 1:32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.2","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:2","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Nous savons, en effet, que le jugement de Dieu contre ceux qui commettent de telles choses est selon la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.3","name":"Romains 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.1","name":"Romains 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.3","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:3","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et penses-tu, \u00f4 homme, qui juges ceux qui commettent de telles choses, et qui les fais, que tu \u00e9chapperas au jugement de Dieu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.4","name":"Romains 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.2","name":"Romains 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.4","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:4","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ou m\u00e9prises-tu les richesses de sa bont\u00e9, de sa patience et de sa longanimit\u00e9, ne reconnaissant pas que la bont\u00e9 de Dieu te pousse \u00e0 la repentance?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.5","name":"Romains 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.3","name":"Romains 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.5","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:5","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mais, par ton endurcissement et par ton c\u0153ur imp\u00e9nitent, tu t\u2019amasses un tr\u00e9sor de col\u00e8re pour le jour de la col\u00e8re et de la manifestation du juste jugement de Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.6","name":"Romains 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.4","name":"Romains 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.6","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:6","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>qui rendra \u00e0 chacun selon ses \u0153uvres;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.7","name":"Romains 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.5","name":"Romains 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.7","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:7","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>r\u00e9servant la vie \u00e9ternelle \u00e0 ceux qui, par la pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance \u00e0 bien faire, cherchent l\u2019honneur, la gloire et l\u2019immortalit\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.8","name":"Romains 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.6","name":"Romains 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.8","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:8","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>mais l\u2019irritation et la col\u00e8re \u00e0 ceux qui, par esprit de dispute, sont rebelles \u00e0 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 et ob\u00e9issent \u00e0 l\u2019injustice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.9","name":"Romains 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.7","name":"Romains 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.9","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:9","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Tribulation et angoisse sur toute \u00e2me d\u2019homme qui fait le mal, sur le Juif premi\u00e8rement, puis sur le Grec!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.10","name":"Romains 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.8","name":"Romains 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.10","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:10","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Gloire, honneur et paix pour quiconque fait le bien, pour le Juif premi\u00e8rement, puis pour le Grec!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.11","name":"Romains 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.9","name":"Romains 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.11","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:11","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Car devant Dieu il n\u2019y a point d\u2019acception de personnes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.12","name":"Romains 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.10","name":"Romains 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.12","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:12","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Tous ceux qui ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9 sans la loi p\u00e9riront aussi sans la loi, et tous ceux qui ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9 avec la loi seront jug\u00e9s par la loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.13","name":"Romains 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.11","name":"Romains 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.13","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:13","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ce ne sont pas, en effet, ceux qui \u00e9coutent la loi qui sont justes devant Dieu, mais ce sont ceux qui la mettent en pratique qui seront justifi\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.14","name":"Romains 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.12","name":"Romains 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.14","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:14","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Quand les pa\u00efens, qui n\u2019ont point la loi, font naturellement ce que prescrit la loi, ils sont, eux qui n\u2019ont point la loi, une loi pour eux-m\u00eames;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.15","name":"Romains 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.13","name":"Romains 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.15","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:15","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>ils montrent que l\u2019\u0153uvre de la loi est \u00e9crite dans leurs c\u0153urs, leur conscience en rendant t\u00e9moignage, et leurs pens\u00e9es s\u2019accusant ou se d\u00e9fendant tour \u00e0 tour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.16","name":"Romains 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.14","name":"Romains 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.16","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:16","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>C\u2019est ce qui para\u00eetra au jour o\u00f9, selon mon \u00c9vangile, Dieu jugera par J\u00e9sus-Christ les actions secr\u00e8tes des hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.17","name":"Romains 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.15","name":"Romains 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.17","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:17","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les Juifs<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-24: cf. J\u00e9 8:8, 9. Ja 4:16, 17. Ro 14:15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Toi qui te donnes le nom de Juif, qui te reposes sur la loi, qui te glorifies de Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.18","name":"Romains 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.16","name":"Romains 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.18","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:18","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>qui connais sa volont\u00e9, qui appr\u00e9cies la diff\u00e9rence des choses, \u00e9tant instruit par la loi;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.19","name":"Romains 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.17","name":"Romains 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.19","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:19","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>toi qui te flattes d\u2019\u00eatre le conducteur des aveugles, la lumi\u00e8re de ceux qui sont dans les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.20","name":"Romains 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.18","name":"Romains 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.20","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:20","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>le docteur des insens\u00e9s, le ma\u00eetre des ignorants, parce que tu as dans la loi la r\u00e8gle de la science et de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.21","name":"Romains 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.19","name":"Romains 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.21","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:21","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>toi donc, qui enseignes les autres, tu ne t\u2019enseignes pas toi-m\u00eame! Toi qui pr\u00eaches de ne pas d\u00e9rober, tu d\u00e9robes!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.22","name":"Romains 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.20","name":"Romains 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.22","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:22","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Toi qui dis de ne pas commettre d\u2019adult\u00e8re, tu commets l\u2019adult\u00e8re! Toi qui as en abomination les idoles, tu commets des sacril\u00e8ges!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.23","name":"Romains 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.21","name":"Romains 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.23","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:23","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Toi qui te fais une gloire de la loi, tu d\u00e9shonores Dieu par la transgression de la loi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.24","name":"Romains 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.22","name":"Romains 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.24","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:24","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Car le nom de Dieu est \u00e0 cause de vous blasph\u00e9m\u00e9 parmi les pa\u00efens, comme cela est \u00e9crit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.25","name":"Romains 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.23","name":"Romains 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.25","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:25","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-29: cf. (J\u00e9 4:4. Jn 1:48. Ro 4:11, 12.) (1 Co 7:19. Ga 5:6.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>La circoncision est utile, si tu mets en pratique la loi; mais si tu transgresses la loi, ta circoncision devient incirconcision.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.26","name":"Romains 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.24","name":"Romains 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.26","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:26","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Si donc l\u2019incirconcis observe les ordonnances de la loi, son incirconcision ne sera-t-elle pas tenue pour circoncision?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.27","name":"Romains 2:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.25","name":"Romains 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.27","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:27","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>L\u2019incirconcis de nature, qui accomplit la loi, ne te condamnera-t-il pas, toi qui la transgresses, tout en ayant la lettre de la loi et la circoncision?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.28","name":"Romains 2:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.26","name":"Romains 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.28","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:28","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le Juif, ce n\u2019est pas celui qui en a les dehors; et la circoncision, ce n\u2019est pas celle qui est visible dans la chair.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.29","name":"Romains 2:29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.27","name":"Romains 2:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.29","label":"","reference":"Romains 2:29","prev_osis_id":"Rom.002.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.2.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Mais le Juif, c\u2019est celui qui l\u2019est int\u00e9rieurement; et la circoncision, c\u2019est celle du c\u0153ur, selon l\u2019esprit et non selon la lettre. La louange de ce Juif ne vient pas des hommes, mais de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.2","name":"Romains 2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.3.1","name":"Romains 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.28","name":"Romains 2:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb9b9b902.62524544');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9b9b902.62524544\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb9b9b902.62524544","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb9b9b902.62524544'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9b9b902.62524544\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}